snippet.title: Need For Cheese - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1123240/Need_For_Cheese/
Action rpg Dungeon-Crawler currently in development. Explore a weird planet, fight your way through the underground and figure stuff out :/
(early game footage)

Our Composer: TobiWeiss, @filmandgamemusic - http://www.filmandgamemusic.com
Game: @GreenGooGames, @NeedForCheese - http://www.nfcgame.net
https://linktr.ee/NeedForCheese

** feel free to use the audio if featuring the game on your channel ** :)

(work in progress)

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1123240/Need_For_Cheese/
